data.description: Wonderful home in the Rapids with neighborhood pool, clubhouse, tennis courts & greeneway access! This home is fabulous with endless possibilities but needs a little TLC and someone to bring it back to life! Large lot with creek that runs behind with view from the deck! Kitchen with island, granite countertops & breakfast room with bay window! Living room with fireplace & built ins! Dining room crown molding & wainscoting! Office or sitting room with crown molding! Owner suite with large bathroom & walk in closet! Spacious spare bedrooms, one with private sitting area! Nearby full bathroom! Lovely foyer with closet & half bath for guests! Side entry 2 car garage! Fantastic location with easy access to downtown, I-20, SRS & more!
